    <h1>1 AL&#xAD;TER&#xAD;NA&#xAD;TIVE/IN&#xAD;DIE ROCK DOWN IN THE WEEDS, WHERE THE WORLD ONCE WAS</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
